Ross Patterson and Dan Hollaway break down Tulsi Gabbard’s new bill that wants to ban biological males from competing against girls in high school, they dive into the allegations against Shia LaBeouf — including that he killed stray dogs for method acting, Dan tells a story about Sean Penn being worthless during Hurricane Katrina, plus the Drinkin’ Bro of the Week and Andrew Yang running for NYC mayor.
